long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MedDict is a medical dictionary made by VinUnians for College of Health Sciences (CHS) students & faculties in VinUniversity. The dictionary is curated by Professor Huynh Dinh Chien, faculty of CHS at VinUniversity. 

This plugin searches for both English/Vietnamese medical words to receive the corresponding words in the other language and provides sample illustrations to the words.
